channel.title: Symon's Dinners Cooking Out
channel.desc: Michael Symon is ready to relax outdoors in style; he starts with the classic Trout Almondine before preparing mouthwatering Fondant Potatoes; he mixes up a Green Bean and Radicchio Salad, and Liz toasts the night with a Black Velvet cocktail.
